3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a method for learning discriminant low-rank representations, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence.

5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The proposed method is evaluated on image and face-related tasks, which are common in multimedia research.
